          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Department of Veterans Affairs Emergency Medical Staffing Recruitment and Retention Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to modify the hours of employment for a physician or physician assistant appointed in the VA on a full-time basis to more or less than 80 hours in a biweekly pay period provided the employee's total hours of employment in a calendar year do not exceed 2,080.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2015-05-21</actionDate>
